text: Marie Laissus (born 7 February 1978) is a French snowboarder. She was born in Savoie. She competed at the 2006 Winter Olympics, in snowboard cross. == References == == External links == * Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Savoie Category:French female snowboarders Category:Olympic snowboarders of France Category:Snowboarders at the 2006 Winter Olympics
